{{Otheruses|Cone}}
The '''cone sock''' was a chemical-based garment created by [[Alyn Rae]] and his team of [[Scientist/Legends|scientists]]. Intended for members of the [[Gotal/Legends|Gotal]] [[Species/Legends|species]], the device was designed to slip over the [[Alien/Legends|aliens]]' head [[cones]], thus blocking out irritating electromagnetic emissions while allowing other transmissions to pass through. While originally expensive, the garment eventually gained more popularity among lower-income Gotals.

